{"tid":1243670,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好以為買杯咖啡要求多多就好型","createTime":"2019-06-19T14:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T14:47:30.000Z","uid":43557,"like":12,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f073529920bf5875c1319b60f6e36f88a9fa4d41","tid":1243670,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"係連鎖coffee shop做緊，成日見d客叫野飲要求多多，以為自己好型，但其實d要求係7嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想開post一次過講返晒比大家知，等大家唔洗做7頭，同行又可以對少d7頭客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申自己唔係識好多，但基本野都識d，歡迎發問嘅<br />\n1.latte係奶咁解，唔係牛奶咖啡，不過叫latte都知你要牛奶咖啡<br />\n2.其他地方唔知，但我做個間caffe latte係冇落糖嘅，唔好再講少糖走糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.matcha latte係抹茶牛奶，係抺茶粉加奶，冇咖啡係入面，試過有個八婆OL客問我有冇咖啡係入面，同佢講完冇又唔撚信，仲要話乜撚野話明latte點解冇咖啡，真係7到世界級<br />\n4.single/double espresso 即係一/兩個shot 嘅咖啡，所以咁平，會用個細杯仔裝，以後唔好再問點解咁細杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係會好7<br />\n5.espresso本身得熱，想要凍可以叫espresso on ice，咁就會加冰比你，但杯野相對會淡咗<br />\n6.Flat White本身冇foam嘅，唔該唔好懶醒叫Flat White no foam，我會係背後笑你on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7.Ristretto Bianco同Flat White得熱，原因應該係同杯野本身原理有關<br />\n8.Ristretto Bianco係拎咗每個shot最濃個part加奶，唔好再問點解咁苦，飲唔到就唔好飲，叫完又屌我地沖得苦得滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時諗到咁多，之後諗到再講<br />\n其實叫咖啡唔明，d員工都好樂意回答，但唔該唔好再用埋晒d西態度，落埋晒d on 9 要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e403b90c94189fac359f1e12384e9c518bdf4740","tid":1243670,"uid":34174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:34:56.000Z","msg":"Pacific coffee 凍飲有糖"},{"pid":"f414a798487b6994cce75df38c8a58fe474d8437","tid":1243670,"uid":134087,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:37:32.000Z","msg":"又bin c"},{"pid":"e3e6c68ccc6ce4ce6a6588064a6cbc3dc8dd2f5b","tid":1243670,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b142c71d7e98353c87531b5b041e9b47d263ac1","tid":1243670,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"做乜回帶"},{"pid":"9da568b97eeb176430e213deab6ee73b4f32dd3f","tid":1243670,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b142c71d7e98353c87531b5b041e9b47d263ac1","tid":1243670,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"做乜回帶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a0e03e98637bcfba3212f2db556a53d960ffbd","tid":1243670,"uid":245409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:41:18.000Z","msg":"點解好似睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048140bfcd9d3df5dade0845e20ab34fbf6102c1","tid":1243670,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:42:20.000Z","msg":"又回帶"},{"pid":"60e7c6d6cd05d981be77cbbd886b145abddfb7d3","tid":1243670,"uid":94274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:43:11.000Z","msg":"Hello partner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6e3ce63549d438b4943fadfcb3f241e558d251","tid":1243670,"uid":218196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f073529920bf5875c1319b60f6e36f88a9fa4d41","tid":1243670,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"係連鎖coffee shop做緊，成日見d客叫野飲要求多多，以為自己好型，但其實d要求係7嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\